<i>Special robbery is a crime that shall be punished by imprison at least five years.</i>

394
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:59,440
How can the culprit who was apprehended red-handed

395
00:37:59,440 --> 00:38:01,860
be free of all charges?

396
00:38:01,860 --> 00:38:06,740
<i>I wouldn't know. Why don't you ask the prosecutor that was in charge then?</i>

397
00:38:06,740 --> 00:38:08,720
<i>Why are you acting like this now?</i>

398
00:38:08,720 --> 00:38:12,990
<i>Let go of the past and stay careful.</i>

399
00:38:12,990 --> 00:38:15,860
<i>And the same incident two separate times!</i>

400
00:38:15,860 --> 00:38:18,460
<i>And please don't take revenge.</i>

401
00:38:22,770 --> 00:38:25,500
What was the date, the day you found Dokgo Yong Gi?

402
00:38:25,500 --> 00:38:28,350
September 26, 2011.

403
00:38:28,350 --> 00:38:30,430
I did a search on the car.

404
00:38:30,430 --> 00:38:33,200
On September 27, it's listed that Dokgo Yong Gi

405
00:38:33,200 --> 00:38:35,480
went in person to go scrap her car.

406
00:38:36,400 --> 00:38:39,610
She was in the hospital, until the 28th.

407
00:38:44,430 --> 00:38:46,900
Hae Gang's urn is empty.

408
00:38:46,900 --> 00:38:50,420
She's alive. I'm going to find her.

409
00:38:51,480 --> 00:38:54,330
This time, properly, without fail, for sure,

410
00:38:54,330 --> 00:38:56,360
<i>I'm going to find Hae Gang.</i>

411
00:38:56,360 --> 00:38:59,530
I'm still certain that Dokgo Yong Gi

412
00:38:59,530 --> 00:39:02,120
is my wife.

413
00:39:03,600 --> 00:39:05,390
I will find out for sure and then act accordingly.

414
00:39:05,390 --> 00:39:08,090
I can't afford to just believe what you tell me,

415
00:39:08,090 --> 00:39:10,430
and then lose her while she's right in front of me.

416
00:39:10,430 --> 00:39:12,240
This one woman.

417
00:39:13,730 --> 00:39:16,870
The woman who you and I both love.

418
00:39:16,870 --> 00:39:20,480
Let's just focus on that woman, and go from there.

419
00:39:20,480 --> 00:39:24,830
Let's throw away our greed, let's throw away our regret.

420
00:39:24,830 --> 00:39:27,800
Let's both just focus on her happiness,

421
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:29,690
and go from there.

422
00:39:31,160 --> 00:39:34,540
Chun Nyeon Pharmaceuticals broke all the rules. What are you going to tell her?

423
00:39:34,540 --> 00:39:38,060
Fake urn, fake columbarium, questionable accident.

424
00:39:38,060 --> 00:39:42,010
I'm telling you your family did that, Cheon Nyeon Pharmaceuticals did that.

425
00:39:42,010 --> 00:39:44,620
Are you going to tell her the truth?

426
00:39:45,900 --> 00:39:48,050
Once you find her and bring her back,

427
00:39:48,050 --> 00:39:50,690
when her memory returns, what are you going to do?

428
00:39:50,690 --> 00:39:54,180
When she remembers you, when she remembers everything,

429
00:39:54,180 --> 00:39:56,680
when that time comes, what is that woman supposed to do?

430
00:39:56,680 --> 00:39:59,880
Have you thought about the shock that she'll experience?

431
00:40:02,540 --> 00:40:04,840
Choi Jin Eon, this time too,

432
00:40:05,780 --> 00:40:09,480
you won't be able to find your wife properly.

433
00:40:09,480 --> 00:40:12,360
And you shouldn't look for her either.

434
00:40:15,250 --> 00:40:18,240
Can you please excuse me?

435
00:40:24,480 --> 00:40:25,960
Hello?

436
00:40:25,960 --> 00:40:30,010
<i>Hello? It's me, Dokgo Yong Gi!</i>

437
00:40:30,810 --> 00:40:33,310
Don't hang up, just give me a minute.

438
00:40:36,080 --> 00:40:38,150
I'll be back after I take this call.

439
00:41:12,880 --> 00:41:15,950
2970.

440
00:41:15,950 --> 00:41:17,610
Did you write it down?

441
00:41:18,290 --> 00:41:21,470
Read it back to me, starting with the address here.

442
00:41:24,230 --> 00:41:27,290
It's not 46. It's 465.

443
00:41:28,910 --> 00:41:32,390
You're probably going to get a call.

444
00:41:32,390 --> 00:41:35,330
Sorry. I really have to work,

445
00:41:35,330 --> 00:41:39,020
You are the only one I can ask as my reference.

446
00:41:39,930 --> 00:41:41,530
What kind of work are you planning to do?

447
00:41:41,530 --> 00:41:44,320
I'll just do whatever job the staffing agency can find.

448
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:46,320
I don't have a lot of options.

449
00:41:46,320 --> 00:41:50,580
<i>I'll come by after I get off of work. Maybe we can have dinner. I'll see you later.</i>

450
00:41:50,580 --> 00:41:53,540
Ah, hey! You don't have to come.

451
00:41:53,540 --> 00:41:56,750
Seok, I'm really okay.

452
00:41:56,750 --> 00:42:00,500
I even lived in China. This is nothing.

453
00:42:02,890 --> 00:42:06,060
I feel so strange.

454
00:42:06,900 --> 00:42:13,350
I feel like I came out from my own coffin, not the MRI Machine.

455
00:42:13,350 --> 00:42:19,290
I'm not very good at offering words of comfort, Mother.

456
00:42:19,290 --> 00:42:22,890
I don't think I can bear to tell you to have strength either.

457
00:42:22,890 --> 00:42:25,210
Nor do I have anything particular to say.

458
00:42:25,210 --> 00:42:28,680
Instead, I'll come with you to the hospital.

459
00:42:28,680 --> 00:42:32,730
Without Jin Eon being involved, if that's what you want.

460
00:42:32,730 --> 00:42:37,600
So that you don't have to feel scared or lonely, all by yourself.

461
00:42:39,150 --> 00:42:42,880
Thank you. More than any words of comfort,

462
00:42:42,880 --> 00:42:46,120
that gives me strength and comforts me.

463
00:42:48,280 --> 00:42:51,010
Do you want to go watch a movie?

464
00:42:52,870 --> 00:42:58,380
